Trigger AI qualification for a single lead (web fetch + AI rescore). The operation is asynchronous — results take ~60s. `forceFetch:true` re-runs even if recent data exists.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} low-level — when you need to kick qualification on exactly one lead without composite orchestration.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} as the agent's bulk-qualify path — use leadbay_bulk_qualify_leads, which paginates past already-qualified leads, fans out, polls, and bails out cleanly on 429.

